hadiths[158]{hadithnumber,text}:
1237,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (ke khuwab mein) mere paas mere rab ka aik aaney wala ( farishta ( aaya. usne mujhey khabar di, ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke usne mujhey khushkhabri di ke meri ummat mein se jo koi us haal mein marey ke Allah Taala ke sath us ne koi Sharik na thehraya ho to wo jannat mein jaeyga is par maine puchha bhale hi usne zina kya ho, bhale hi usne chori ki ho? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, bhale hi usne zina kya ho bhale hi chori ki ho."
1238,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs us haalat mein marey ke kisi ko Allah ka Sharik thahraataa tha to wo jahannam mein jaeyga aur main ye kehta hun ke jo us haal mein maraa ke Allah ka koi Sharik na thahraataa ho wo jannat mein jaeyga
1239,"hamein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saat (7) kaamon ka hukm diya aur saat (7) kaamon se rokaa. hamein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya tha janaaze ke sath chalney, mareez ka haal poochhney, dawat qabool karney, mazloom ki madad karney ka, qism poori karney ka, salam ka jawab dene ka, chheenk par) يرحمک الله ( kehney ka aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein mana kya tha chandi ke bartan (iste'maal mein laaney) se, soney ki anguthi pahnney se, resham aur deebaaj (ke kapdon ke pahnney) se, Qassii se, istibraq (makhmal) se."
1240,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke musalman ke musalman par panch haq hain: salam ka jawab denaa, mareez ka mizaaj malum karnaa, janazey ke sath chalnaa, dawat qabool karnaa, aur chheenk par (الحمدلله) ke jawab mein) (يرحمک الله) kahnaa. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Abdur-Razzaq ne ki hai. unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey Mamar ne khabar di thi aur uski riwayat Sulaamaa ne bhi Aqeel se ki hai."
1241,"(jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gai) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) apne ghar se jo Sunh mein tha ghodey par Sawar ho kar aaey aur utartey hi masjid mein tashrif ley gaey. phir aap kisi se guftgu kiye baghair Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre mein aaey ( jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki laash Mubarak rakhi hui thi) aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko burde-Hibra ( Yaman ki bani hui dhaarii daar chadar ( se dhaank diya gaya tha. phir aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak khola aur jhuk kar iska bosa liya aur roney lagey. aap ne kaha mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon aey Allah ke Nabi ! Allah Taala 2 mautein aap par kabhi jama nahi karega . siwa aik maut ke jo aap ke muqaddar mein thi, so aap wafat pa chukey. abu-Salma ne kaha ke mujhey Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) jab bahar tashrif laey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) us waqt logon se kuchh baatein kar rahe they. siddeeq akbar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke baith jao. lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) nahi maaney. phir dobara aapne baithney ke liye kaha, lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) nahi maaney. aakhir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kalima shahadat padha to tamam majma' aap ki taraf mutwajjeh ho gaya aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko chhod diya. aap ne farmaya ammaa ba'd! agar koi shakhs tum mein se Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ibadat karta tha to usey malum hona chahiye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho chuki aur agar koi Allah Taala ki ibadat karta hai to Allah Taala baqi rehney wala hai. kabhi wo marney wala nahi. Allah paak ne farmaya hai ''aur Muhammad sirf Allah ke rasool hain aur bahut se rasool us se pahley bhi guzar chukey hain'' ( الشاكرين ( tak (aap ne aayat tilawat ki). qasam Allah ki aisa malum hua ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke aayat ki tilawat se pahley jaisey logon ko malum hi na tha ke ye aayat bhi Allah paak ne Quran Majeed mein utari hai. ab tamam sahaba ne ye aayat aap se seekh li phir to har shakhs ki zaban par yahi aayat thi."
1242,"(jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gai) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) apne ghar se jo Sunh mein tha ghodey par Sawar ho kar aaey aur utartey hi masjid mein tashrif ley gaey. phir aap kisi se guftgu kiye baghair Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre mein aaey ( jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki laash Mubarak rakhi hui thi) aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko burde-Hibra ( Yaman ki bani hui dhaarii daar chadar ( se dhaank diya gaya tha. phir aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak khola aur jhuk kar iska bosa liya aur roney lagey. aap ne kaha mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon aey Allah ke Nabi ! Allah Taala 2 mautein aap par kabhi jama nahi karega . siwa aik maut ke jo aap ke muqaddar mein thi, so aap wafat pa chukey. abu-Salma ne kaha ke mujhey Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) jab bahar tashrif laey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) us waqt logon se kuchh baatein kar rahe they. siddeeq akbar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke baith jao. lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) nahi maaney. phir dobara aapne baithney ke liye kaha, lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) nahi maaney. aakhir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kalima shahadat padha to tamam majma' aap ki taraf mutwajjeh ho gaya aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko chhod diya. aap ne farmaya ammaa ba'd! agar koi shakhs tum mein se Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ibadat karta tha to usey malum hona chahiye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho chuki aur agar koi Allah Taala ki ibadat karta hai to Allah Taala baqi rehney wala hai. kabhi wo marney wala nahi. Allah paak ne farmaya hai ''aur Muhammad sirf Allah ke rasool hain aur bahut se rasool us se pahley bhi guzar chukey hain'' ( الشاكرين ( tak (aap ne aayat tilawat ki). qasam Allah ki aisa malum hua ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke aayat ki tilawat se pahley jaisey logon ko malum hi na tha ke ye aayat bhi Allah paak ne Quran Majeed mein utari hai. ab tamam sahaba ne ye aayat aap se seekh li phir to har shakhs ki zaban par yahi aayat thii."
1243,"ummul-Ulaa (rz), Ansar ki aik aurat ne jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi, ne unhein khabar di ke muhajireen Qura daal kar Ansar mein baant diye gaey to Usmaan-bin-Maz'oon (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey hisse mein aaey. chunanche ham ne unhein apne ghar mein rakha. aakhir wo bimar huey aur usi mein wafat pa gaey. wafat ke baad ghusl diya gaya aur kafan mein lapet diya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey. maine kaha abu-Saaib aap par Allah ki rahmatein hon meri aap ke mutaalliq shahadat ye hai ke Allah Taala ne aap ki izzat farmai hai. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tumhen kaisey malum hua ke Allah Taala ne unki izzat farmai hai? maine kaha ya Rasulullah! mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon phir kis ki Allah Taala izzat afzaai karega? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya usmein shuba nahi ke unki maut aa chukii, qism Allah ki ke main bhi unke liye khair hi ki ummeed rakhta hun lekin Allah ki qasam! mujhey khud apne mutaalliq bhi malum nahi ke mere sath kya mamla hoga. halanke main Allah ka rasool hun. ummul-Ulaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! ab main kabhi kisi ke mutaalliq (is tarah ki) gawahi nahi doongii ."
1244,"jab mere walid Shahid kar diye gaey to main unke chehrey par padaa ho kapda kholtaa aur rotaa tha. doosrey log to mujhey us se roktey they lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuchh nahi keh rahe they. aakhir meri chachii Fatima (Raziallahu anha) bhi roney lagiin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log ro'o ya chup raho. jab tak tum log maiyat ko uthatey nahi malaaika to barabar is par apne paron ka saaya kiye huey hain. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Shoba ke sath ibne-Juraij ne ki, unhein ibne-Munkadir ne khabar di aur unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna."
1245,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najashi ki wafat ki khabar isi din di jis din uski wafat hui thi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhney ki jagah gaey aur logon ke sath saf baandh kar (janaaze ki Namaz mein) char takbeerein kahin .
1246,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Zaid ne jhanda sanbhaalaa lekin wo Shahid ho gaey. phir Jafar ne sanbhaalaa aur wo bhi Shahid ho gaey. phir Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha ne sanbhaalaa aur wo bhi Shahid ho gaey. us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon mein aansu bah rahey they. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (aur phir Khalid-bin Waleed ne khud apne taur par jhanda utha liya aur unko fateh hasil hui.
1247,"aik shakhs ki wafat ho gaee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski iyaadat ko jaya kartey they. chunkey unka intiqal raat mein hua tha isliye raat hi mein logon ne unhein dafn kar diya aur jab subah hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (ke janaaza taiyaar hotey waqt) mujhey bataaney mein (kya ( rukawat thi? logon ne kaha ke raat thi aur andhera bhi tha. isliye ham ne munasib nahi samjha ke kahin aapko takleef ho. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski qabr par tashrif laey aur Namaz padhi."
1248,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi musalman ke agar teen bachchey mar jayen jo bulooghat ko na pahunchey hon to Allah Taala us rehmat ke nateejey mein jawan bachchon se wo rakhta hai musalman ( bachchey ke bap aur maan ( ko bhi jannat mein dakhil karega .
1249,aurton ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darkhaast ki ke hamein bhi nasihat karne ke liye aap aik din khas farma dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unki darkhaast manzoor farmatey huey aik khas din mein) unko waz (nasihat) farmaya aur batlaya ke jis aurat ke teen bachchey mar jayen to wo uske liye jahannam se panah bin jatey hain. is par aik aurat ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! agar kisi ke 2 hi bachchey marein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke 2 bachchon par bhii.
1250,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bhi kaha ke wo bachchey murad hain jo abhi bulooghat ko na pahunchey hun.
1251,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi ke agar teen bachchey mar jayen to wo dozakh mein nahi jaeyga aur agar jaeyga bhi to sirf qism poori karne ke liye. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) farmatey hain. ( Quran ki aayat ye hai) tum mein se har aik ko dozakh ke uper se guzarna hoga.
1252,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik aurat ke paas se guzrey jo aik qabr par baithi hui ro rahi thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya ke Allah se dar aur sabr kar."
1253,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beti (zainab ya umme-kulsoom (Raziallahu anhu)) ki wafat hui Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan tashrif laey aur farmaya ke teen ya panch martaba ghusl de-do aur agar munasib samjho to us se bhi zyada de sakti ho. ghusl ke pani mein berii ke pattey mila lo aur aakhir mein kaafoor ya (ye kaha ke) kuchh kaafoor ka istemal kar lena aur ghusl se farigh honey par mujhey khabar de dena. chunanche ham ne jab ghusl de liya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar dedii . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein apna izaar diya aur farmaya ke usey unki qamees bana do. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad apne izaar se thi.
1254,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beti ko ghusl de rahi thin ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur farmaya ke teen ya panch martaba ghusl do ya us se bhi zyada , pani aur berii ke patton se aur aakhir mein kaafoor bhi istemal karna. phir farigh ho kar mujhey khabar de dena. jab ham farigh huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar kar di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna izaar inayat farmaya aur farmaya ke ye andar iske badan par lapet do."
1255,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beti ke ghusl ke waqt farmaya tha ke daain taraf se aur wuzu waley parts se ghusl shuru karna.
1256,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi ko ham ghusl de rahi thin. jab ham ne ghusl shuru kar diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghusl daain taraf se aur wuzu waley parts se shuru karo.
1257,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik sahibzadi ka intiqal ho gaya. us mauqe par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein farmaya ke tum usey teen ya panch martaba ghusl do aur agar munasib samjho to us se zyada martaba bhi ghusl de sakti ho. phir farigh ho kar mujhey khabar dena. chunanche jab ham ghusl de chukiin to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna izaar inayat farmaya aur farmaya ke usey uske badan se lapet do.
1258,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik beti ka intiqal ho gaya tha. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur farmaya ke usey teen ya panch martaba ghusl de do aur agar tum munasib samjho to us se bhi zyada pani aur berii ke patton se nehlaao aur aakhir mein kaafoor ya (ye kaha ke) kuchh kaafoor ka bhi istemal karna. phir farigh ho kar mujhey khabar dena. umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab ham farigh huey to ham ne kelha bhijwaayaa . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna tehband hamein diya aur farmaya ke usey andar jism par lapet do. Ayub ne Hafsa binte- Sirin se riwayat ki, unse umme-Atiya ne isi tarah hadis bayan ki."
1259,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke teen ya panch ya saat (7) martaba ya agar tum munasib samjho to us se bhi zyada ghusl de sakti ho. Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ham ne unke sar ke baal teen latun mein taqseem kar diye they.
1260,unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi ke baalon ko teen latun mein taqseem kar diya tha. pahley baal kholey gaey phir unhein dho kar unki teen chutiyaan kar di gaiin.
1261,"umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan Ansar ki un khawaateen mein se jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi, aik aurat aai , Basra mein unhein apne aik betey ki talash thi. lekin wo na mila. phir usne ham se ye hadis bayan ki ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi ko ghusl de rahi thin ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur farmaya ke teen ya panch martaba ghusl de do aur agar munasib samjho to us se bhi zyada de sakti ho. ghusl pani aur berii ke patton se hona chahiye aur aakhir mein kaafoor bhi istemal kar lenaa. ghusl se farigh ho kar mujhey khabar kara dena. unhon-ne bayan kya ke jab ham ghusl de chukein (to itlaa di (aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tehband inayat kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey andar badan se lapet do. us se zyada Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh nahi farmaya, mujhey ye nahi malum ke ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kon si beti thin (ye Ayub ne kaha (aur unhon-ne bataya ke) ash'aar (ka matlab ye hai ke usmein laash lapet di jaey. Ibne-Sirin (Rahmatullahi-alaih) bhi yahi farmaya kartey they ke aurat ke badan par usey lapeta jaey izaar ke taur par na baandha jaey."
1262,"ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beti ke sar ke baal goondh kar unki teen chutiyaan kar diin aur Wakee ne Sufiyan se yun riwayat kya, aik peshani ki taraf ke baalon ki chatiyaa aur 2 idhar-udhar ke baalon ki."
1263,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik sahibzadi ka intiqal ho gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur farmaya ke unko pani aur berii ke patton se teen ya panch martaba ghusl de do. agar tum munasib samjho to us se zyada bhi de sakti ho aur aakhir mein kaafoor ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke) thodi si kaafoor istemal karo phir jab ghusl de chuko to mujhey khabar do. chunanche farigh ho kar ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unke kafan ke liye) apna izaar inayat kya. ham ne iske sar ke baalon ki teen chutiyaan karke unhein peechhey ki taraf daal diya tha.
1264,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Yaman ke teen safaid sootii dhuley huey kapdon mein kafan diya gaya unmein na qamees thi na amaamaa.
1265,aik shakhs maidan Arfa main ( ehram baandhey huey) khada hua tha ke apni sawari se gir padaa aur sawari ne unhein kuchal diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye farmaya ke pani aur berii ke patton se ghusl de kar do kapdon mein unhein kafan do aur ye bhi hidayat farmai ke unhein khushbu na lagaao aur na unka sar chhipaao. kyonke ye qiyamat ke din labbaik kehta hua uthey ga.
1266,"aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maidan Arfa mein waquf kiye huey tha ke wo apne oont se gir padaa aur oont ne unhein kuchal diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein pani aur berii ke patton se ghusl de kar do kapdon ka kafan do, khushbu na lagaao aur na sar dhako kyonke Allah Taala qiyamat ke din unhein labbaik kehtey huey uthaaega."
1267,aik martaba ham log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ehram baandhey huey they ke aik shakhs ki gardan iske oont ne tod daalii. to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein pani aur berii ke patton se ghusl de do aur kapdon ka kafan do aur khushbu na lagaao na unke sar ko dhako . isliye ke Allah Taala unhein uthaaega. us haalat mein ke wo labbaik pukarta hoga.
1268,"aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maidan Arafaat mein khada hua tha, achcha wo apni sawari se gir padaa. Ayub ne kaha ontni ne uski gardan tod dali aur Amr ne yun kaha ke ontni ne usko girtey hi mar daala aur iska intiqal ho gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey pani aur berii ke patton se ghusl do aur 2 kapdon ka kafan do aur khushbu na lagaao na sar dhako kyonke qiyamat mein ye uthaya jaeyga Ayub ne kaha ke (yaani) talbiya kehtey huey ( uthaya jaaeyga) aur Amr ne (apni riwayat main ( malbii (ke bajaey) ( mulbiyaa (ka lafz naql kya. (yani labbaik kehta hua uthega ( ."
1269,jab Abdullah-bin-Ubai ( munafiq ( ki maut hui to uska betaa ( Abdullah sahabi ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah! walid ke kafan ke liye aap apni qamees inayat farmaiye aur un par Namaz padhiye aur maghfirat ki dua keejiye. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni qamees (bahut hi mohabbat ki wjah se) inayat ki aur farmaya ke mujhey batana mein namaaze-janaaza padhunga. Abdullah ne itlaa bhijwaai. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhaaney ke liye aagey badhey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko peechhey se pakad liya aur arz kya ke kya Allah Taala ne aapko munaafeqeen ki namaaze-janaaza padhney se mana nahi kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey ikhtiyar diya gaya hai jaisa ke irshad baari hai ''tu unke liye istighfar kar ya na kar aur agar to 70 martaba bhi istighfar karey to bhi Allah unhein hargiz maaf nahi karega'' chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai. iske baad ye aayat utri ''kisi bhi munafiq ki maut par uski namaaze-janaaza kabhi na padhaanaa''.
1270,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to Abdullah-bin-Ubai ko dafn kya ja raha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey qabr se nikalwaayaa aur apna luaab dahan iske munh mein daala aur apni qamees pahnaaii.
1271,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko teen sootii dhuley huey kapdon ka kafan diya gaya tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kafan mein na qamees thi aur na amaamaa.
1272,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko teen kapdon mein kafan diya gaya tha jin mein na qamees thi aur na amama tha. imam abu-Adbullah Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) farmatey hain ke abu-Nueim ne lafz ( ثلاثة ( nahi kaha aur Abdullaah-bin-Waleed ne Sufiyan se lafz ( ثلاثة ( naql kya hai.
1273,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sahwal ke teen safaid kapdon ka kafan diya gaya tha na unmein qamees thi aur na amama tha.
1274,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney aik din khana rakha gaya to unhon-ne farmaya ke Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu) (Uhud ki jang mein) Shahid huey, wo mujh se afzal they. lekin unke kafan ke liye aik chadar ke siwa aur koi cheez muhaiya na ho sakii. isi tarah jab Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) Shahid huey ya kisi doosrey sahabi ka naam liya, wo bhi mujh se afzal they. lekin unke kafan ke liye bhi sirf aik hi chadar mil sakii. mujhey to dar lagta hai ke kahin aisa na ho ke hamarey chain aur aaraam ke saman ham ko jaldi se duniya hi mein de diye gaey hon phir wo roney lagey."
1275,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney khana hazir kya gaya. wo rozey se they us waqt unhon-ne farmaya ke haaye ! Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu) Shahid kiye gaey, wo mujh se behtar they. lekin unke kafan ke liye sirf aik chadar muyassar aa saki ke agar us se unka sar dhanka jata to paon khul jatey aur paon dhaankey jatey to sar khul jata aur main samajhta hun ke unhon-ne ye bhi farmaya aur Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) bhi (usi tarah) Shahid huey wo bhi mujh se achchhey they. phir unke baad duniya ki kushadgi hamarey liye khub hui ya ye farmaya ke duniya hamein bahut di gaee aur hamein to uska dar lagta hai ke kahin aisa na ho ke hamari nekiyon ka badla isi duniya mein ham ko mil gaya ho phir aap is tarah roney lagey ke khana bhi chhod diya."
1276,ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sirf Allah ke liye hijrat ki. ab hamein Allah Taala se ajr milnaa hi tha. hamarey kuchh sathi to intiqal kar gaey aur (is duniya mein) unhon-ne apne kiye ka koi phal nahi dekha. Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unhiin logon mein se they aur hamarey kuchh sathiyon ka mewa paak gaya aur wo chun-chun kar khata hai. (Mus'ab-bin-Umair (rz)) Uhud ki ladai mein Shahid huey ham ko unke kafan mein aik chadar ke siwa aur koi cheez na mili aur wo bhi aisi ke agar us se sar chhipaatey hain to paon khul jata hai aur agar paon dhaktey to sar khul jata. aakhir ye dekh kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya ke sar ko chipa dein aur paon par sabz ghaas izkhir naam ke daal dein.
1277,"aik aurat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik bani hui haashiya daar chadar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye tohfa laaii. Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( haaziriin se) puchha ke tum jantey ho chadar kiya? logon ne kaha ke ji haan ! shamla . Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha haan shamla (tum ne theek bataya ( khair us aurat ne kaha ke maine apne hath se isey bunaa hai aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pahnaaney ke liye laai hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo kapda qabool kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski us waqt zarurat bhi thi phir usey izaar (Tehband) ke taur par baandh kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey to aik sahib (Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha ke ye to badi achi chadar hai, ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey pehna dijiye. logon ne kaha ke aap ne (maang kar) kuchh achchha nahi kya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey apni zarurat ki wjah se pehna tha aur tum ne ye maang liya halanke tum ko malum hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi ka sawal radd nahi kartey. Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke Allah ki qasam! maine apne pahnney ke liye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye chadar nahi mangi thi. balke mein usey apna kafan banaaunga. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke wahi chadar unka kafan banii."
1278,hamein (aurton ko) janazey ke sath chalney se mana kya gaya magar takeed se mana nahi hua.
1279,umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik betey ka intiqal ho gaya. intiqal ke teesrey din unhon-ne ''Safra khalooq'' (eik qism ki zard khushboo) mangwai aur usey apne badan par lagaya aur farmaya ke khawind ke siwa kisi doosrey par teen din se zyada sog karne se hamein mana kya gaya hai.
1280,Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ki khabar jab Sham (Syria) se aai to Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu)) Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ki sahibzadi aur Ummul-Momenin ( ne teesrey din ''Safra'' ( khushbu ( mangwa kar apne donon rukhsaaron aur baazuon par malaa aur farmaya ke agar maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye na suna hota ke koi bhi aurat jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhti ho uske liye jaaiz nahi hai ke wo shauhar ke siwa kisi ka sog teen din se zyada manaaey aur shauhar ka sog char mahiney das din kare. to mujhey us waqt us khushbu ke istemal ki zarurat nahi thi.
1281,wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaee to unhon-ne farmaya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke koi bhi aurat jo Allah aur yaum aakhirat par eman rakhti ho uske liye shauhar ke siwa kisi murdey par bhi teen din se zyada sog manaanaa jaaiz nahi hai. haan shauhar par char mahiney das din tak sog manaaey.
1282,"phir main Zainab-bint-Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaee jabke unke bhai ka intiqal hua, unhon-ne khushbu mangwai aur usey lagaayaa, phir farmaya ke mujhey khushbu ki koi zarurat na thi lekin maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko member par ye kehtey huey suna hai ke kisi bhi aurat ko jo Allah aur yaume-aakhirat par eman rakhti ho, jaaiz nahi hai ke kisi maiyat par teen din se zyada sog kare. lekin shauhar ka sog (iddat) char mahiney das din tak kare."
1283,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar aik aurat par hua jo qabr par baithi ro rahi thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah se dar aur sabr kar. wo bolii jao ji parey hato. ye museebat tum par padi hoti to pata chalta . wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pehchan na saki thi. phir jab logon ne usey bataya ke ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) they, to ab wo ( ghabraa kar) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darwaza par pahunchi . wahan usey koi darbaan na mila. phir usne kaha ke main aapko pehchan na saki thi. ( maaf farmaiye) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sabr to jab sadma shuru ho us waqt karna chahiye ( ab kya hota hai)."
1284,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik sahibzadi ( Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ( ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko itlaa karaai ke mera aik ladka marney ke qareeb hai, isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laaein . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein salam kahlwaayaa aur kahlwaayaa ke Allah Taala hi ka Sara maal hai, jo ley liya wo usi ka tha aur jo usney diya wo bhi usi ka tha aur har cheez uski bargah se waqt muqarrara par hi waaqe hoti hai. isliye sabr karo aur Allah Taala se sawab ki ummeed rakho. phir Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne qism de kar apne yahan bulwa bhejaa. ab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) janey ke liye uthey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sa'd-bin-Ubaada, Muaaz-bin-Jabal, Ubaii-bin-Ka'b, Zaid-bin-Saabit aur bahut se doosrey sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. bachchey ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney kya gaya. jiski jaan-kunii ka aalim tha. abu-Usman ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ke Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke jaisey puraanaa mishkeeza hota hai (aur pani ke takraaney ki andar se awaz hoti hai. isi tarah jaan-kunii ke waqt bachche ke halaq se awaz aa rahi thi) ye dekh kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon se aansu bah nikley. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) bol uthey ke ya Rasulullah! ye ronaa kaisa hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to Allah ki rehmat hai ke jisey Allah Taala ne apne ( nek ( bandon ke dilon mein rakha hai aur Allah Taala bhi apne un raham dil bandon par raham farmata hai jo dusron par raham kartey hain."
1285,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik beti (umme-kulsoom (rz)) ke janaaze mein hazir they. (wo Usman ghanii (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi thin. jinka 5 Hijri mein intiqal hua) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabr par baithey huey they. unhon-ne kaha ke maine dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhen aansuon se bhar aai thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne poochha. kya tum mein koi aisa shakhs bhi hai ke jo aaj ki raat aurat ke paas na gaya ho. is par abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir qabr main tum utro. chunanche wo unki qabr mein utrey .
1286,Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik sahibzadi (umme-Abaan) ka Makka mein intiqal ho gaya tha. ham bhi unke janazey mein hazir huey. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bhi tashrif laey. mein un donon hazraat ke darmyan mein betha hua tha ya ye kaha ke main aik buzurg ke qareeb baith gaya aur doosrey buzurg baad mein aaey aur mere bazu mein baith gaey. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Amr-bin-Usmaan se kaha (jo umme-Abaan ke bhai they) roney se kyon nahi roktey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne to farmaya hai ke maiyat par ghar walon ke roney se azab hota hai.
1287,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi aisa hi farmaya tha. phir aap bayan karne lagey ke main umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Makka se chala jab ham beda tak pahunchey to samney aik babool ke darakht ke nichey chand sawar nazar padey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ja kar dekho to sahii ye kon log hain. unka bayan hai ke maine dekha to Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) they. phir jab uski itlaa di to aap ne farmaya ke unhein bula laao. main Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas dobara aaya aur kaha ke chaliye ameerul-momineen bulatey hain. chunanche wo khidmat mein hazir huey. (khair ye qissa to ho chukaa) phir jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) zakhmi kiye gaey to Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) rotey huey andar dakhil huey. wo keh rahe they haaye mere bhai! haaye mere saahib! is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Suheb (rz)! tum mujh par rotey ho, tum nahi jantey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke maiyat par uske ghar walon ke roney se azab hota hai."
1288,jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka intiqal ho gaya to maine us hadis ka zikr Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kya. unhon-ne farmaya ke rehmat umr (Raziallahu anhu) par ho. b-khudaa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye nahi farmaya hai ke Allah momin par iske ghar walon ke roney ki wjah se azab karega balke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun farmaya ke Allah Taala kaafir ka azab iske ghar walon ke roney ki wjah se aur zyada kar deta hai. iske baad kehney lagiin ke Quran ki ye aayat tum ko bas karti hai ke ''koii kisi ke gunah ka zimme daar aur iska bojh uthaney wala nahi.'' is par Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne us waqt (yani umme-Abaan ke janazey mein) sura Najm ki ye aayat padhii'' aur Allah hi hansaataa hai aur wahi rulaataa hai.'' ibne-abi-Mulaika ne kaha ke Allah ki qasam! Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye taqreer sun kar ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kuchh jawab nahi diya.
1289,"ham se Abdullaah-bin-Yoosuf Taneesii ne bayan kya, unhein Imam Malik ne khabar di, unhein Abdullah-bin abi-Bakr ne, unhein unke bap ne aur unhein Umra-binte-Abdur-Rehmaan ne, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki biwi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna. aap ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar aik Yahudi aurat par hua jiske marney par iske ghar waley ro rahe they. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye log ro rahe hain halanke usko qabr mein azab kya ja raha hai."
1290,"jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko zakhmi kya gaya to Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ye kehtey huey aaey, haaye mere bhai! is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke kya tujh ko malum nahi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai ke murdey ko uske ghar walon ke roney se azab kya jata hai."
1291,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke mere mutaalliq koi jhooti baat kehna aam logon se mutaalliq jhoot bolney ki tarah nahi hai jo shakhs bhi jaan-bojh kar mere uper jhoot boley wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley. aur maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye bhi suna ke kisi maiyat par agar nauha w maatam kya jaey to us nauha ki wjah se bhi is par azab hota hai.
1292,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maiyat ko is par nauha kiye janey ki wjah se bhi qabr mein azab hota hai. abdaan ke sath us hadis ko Abdul-Aala ne bhi Yazeed-bin-Zaree' se riwayat kya. unhon-ne kaha ham se Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Qatada ne aur Aadam-bin-abii-Ayaas ne Shoba se yun riwayat kya ke maiyat par zindey ke roney se azab hota hai."
1293,"mere walid ki laash Uhud ke maidan se laai gaee. (mushrikon ne) aap ki sura tak bigaad di thi. laash Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney rakhi gaee. uper se aik kapda dhakaa hua tha, maine chaha ke kapdey ko hataaun. lekin meri qaum ne mujhey rokaa. phir dobara kapda hataaney ki koshish ki. us martaba bhi meri qaum ne mujh ko rok diya. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se janaaza uthaya gaya. us waqt kisi zor-zor se roney waley ki awaz sunai di to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke ye kon hai? logon ne kaha ke ye Amr ki beti ya (ye kaha ke) Amr ki behan hain. (naam mein Sufiyan ko shak hua tha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke roti kyon hain? ya ye farmaya ke ro'o nahi ke malaaika barabar apne paron ka saaya kiye rahe hain jab tak iska janaaza uthaya gaya."
1294,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo auratein (kisi ki maut par) apne chehron ko peet'tii aur garebaan chaak kar leti hain aur jahiliyat ki baatein bakti hain wo ham mein se nahi hain.
1295,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hijjatul-wada ke saal ( 10 hijri mein) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laey. mein sakht bimar tha. maine kaha ke mera marz shiddat ikhtiyar kar chuka hai mere paas maal w asbaab bahut hai aur meri sirf aik ladki hai jo waaris hogi to kya main apne 2 tehai maal ko khairat kar dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. maine kaha aadhaa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik tehai kar do aur ye bhi badi khairat hai ya bahut khairat hai agar to apne waarison ko apne peechhey maaldaar chhod jaey to ye us se behtar hoga ke mohtaajii mein unhein is tarah chhod kar jaey ke wo logon ke samney hath phailaatey phirein. ye yad rakho ke jo kharch bhi tum Allah ki raza ki niyat se karogey to is par bhi tumhen sawab milega. yahan tak ke us luqme par bhi jo tum apni biwi ke munh mein rakho. phir maine puchha ke ya Rasulullah! mere sathi to mujhey chhod kar (hijjatul-wadaa karke) Makka se ja rahe hain aur main unse peechhey reh raha hun. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yahan reh kar bhi agar tum koi nek amal karogey to us se tumharey darjey buland hongey aur shayad abhi tum zinda rahogey aur bahut se logon ko (musalmanon ko) tum se fayda pahunchega aur bahuton ko (kuffaar w murtadeen ko) nuqsaan. (phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmaaii) aey Allaah! mere sathiyon ko hijrat par istiqlaal ata farma aur unke qadam peechhey ki taraf na lautaa. lekin museebat zada Sad bin Khaula they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke Makka mein wafat pa janey ki wjah se izhaare-gham kiya tha.
1296,"abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bimar padey, aisey ke un par ghashii taarii thi aur unka sar unki aik biwi umme-abdullaah binte- abi Roma ki god mein tha (wo aik zor ki cheekh mar kar roney lagii) abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) us waqt kuchh bol na sakey lekin jab unko hosh hua to unhon-ne farmaya ke main bhi us kaam se bezaar hon jis se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bezaarii ka izhar farmaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (kisi gham ke waqt) chilla kar roney waali, sar mundwaaney wali aur garebaan chaak karne wali aurton se apni bezaarii ka izhar farmaya tha."
1297,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs (kisi maiyat par) apne rukhsar peetey, garebaan phaadey aur ahade-jaahiliyat ki si baatein karey wo ham mein se nahi hai."
1298,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo (kisi ki maut par) apne rukhsar peetey, garebaan chaak karey aur jahiliyat ki baatein karey wo ham mein se nahi hai."
1299,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Zaid-bin-Haarisa , Jafar aur Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ( Mautaa ki jang mein) ki khabar mili , to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt is tarah tashrif farma they ke gham ke aasaar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey par zahir they. main darwazey ke suraakh se dekh rahi thi. itney mein aik sahib aaey aur Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ki aurton ke roney ka zikr kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein roney se mana kar de. wo gaey lekin wapas aa kar kaha ke wo to nahi maantiin . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke unhein mana kar de. ab wo teesri martaba wapas huey aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! qism Allah ki wo to ham par ghalib aa gaee hain ( Umra ne kaha ke) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko yaqin hua ke (unke us kehney par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir unke munh mein mitti jhonk de. is par maine kaha ke tera bura ho. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ab jis kaam ka hukm de rahe hain wo to karogey nahi lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko takleef mein daal diya."
1300,jab qaariyon ki aik jamat Shahid kar di gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik maheene tak qunoot padhtey rahe. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kabhi nahi dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un dinon se zyada kabhi ghamgeen rahe hun.
1301,abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik bachcha bimar ho gaya unhon-ne kaha ke iska intiqal bhi ho gaya. us waqt abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ghar mein maujood na they. unki biwi (Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu)) ne jab dekha ke bachchey ka intiqal ho gaya to unhon-ne kuchh khana taiyaar kya aur bachchey ko ghar ke aik koney mein lita diya. jab abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey to unhon-ne puchha ke bachchey ki tabeeat kaisi hai? Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke usey aaraam mil gaya hai aur mera khayal hai ke ab wo aaraam hi kar raha hoga. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne samjha ke wo sahi keh rahi hain. (ab bachcha achchha hai) phir abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas raat guzari aur jab subah hui to ghusl kya lekin jab bahar janey ka irada kya to biwi (Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu)) ne itlaa di ke bachchey ka intiqal ho chuka hai. phir unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi aur aap se Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ka haal bayan kya. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke shayad Allah Taala tum donon ko us raat mein barkat ata farmaeyga. Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya ke Ansar ke aik shakhs ne bataya ke maine abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ki unhiin biwi se nau (9) betey dekhey jo sab ke sab Quran ke aalim they.
1302,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya sabr to wahi hai jo sadma ke shuru mein kya jaey.
1303,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath abu-Yusuf lohaar ke yahan gaey. ye Ibrahim ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahibzadey (Raziallahu anhu)) ko doodh pilaaney wali aaya ke khawind they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ko god mein liya aur piyaar kya aur soonghaa. phir iske baad ham unke yahan phir gaey. dekha ke us waqt Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) dam tod rahe hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhen aansuon se bhar aaein. to Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bol padey ke ya Rasulullah! aur aap bhi logon ki tarah be-sabrii karne lagey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ibne- Auf ! ye be-sabrii nahi ye to rehmat hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dobara roey aur farmaya, aankhon se aansu jari hain aur dil gham se nidhaal hai par zaban se ham kahengey wahi jo hamarey parwardigar ko pasand hai aur aey Ibrahim ! ham tumhari judai se ghamgeen hain. isi hadis ko Moosaa-bin-Ismaaeel ne Sulaimaan-bin-Mugheera se, unse Sabit ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya hai."
1304,"Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) kisi marz mein mubtala huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iyaadat ke liye Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf, Sad-bin-abi-Waqas aur Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath unke yahan tashrif ley gaey. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar gaey to teemaar-daaron ke hujoom mein unhein paya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya wafat ho gaii? logon ne kaha nahi ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (unke marz ki shiddat ko dekh kar) ro padey. logon ne jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko rotey huey dekha to wo sab bhi roney lagey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke suno ! Allah Taala aankhon se aansu nikalney par bhi azab nahi karega aur na dil ke gham par. haan iska azab uski wjah se hota hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zaban ki taraf ishara kya (aur agar us zaban se achi baat nikley to ( ye uski rehmat ka bhi baais bantii hai aur maiyat ko iske ghar walon ke nauha w maatam ki wjah se bhi azab hota hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) maiyat par maatam karne par dandey se maartey , patthar phainktey aur roney walon ke munh mein mitti jhonk detey."
1305,"jab Zaid-bin-Haarisa, Ja'far-bin-abii-Taalib aur Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ki khabar aai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is tarah baithey ke gham ke aasaar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey par numaayaan they mein darwazey ke aik suraakh se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh rahi thi. itney mein aik sahib aaey aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! Jafar ke ghar ki auratein nauha aur maatam kar rahi hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rokney ke liye kaha, wo sahib gaey lekin phir wapas aagey aur kaha ke wo nahi maantiin . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dobara rokney ke liye bhejaa. wo gaey aur phir wapas chaley aaey. kaha ke b-khudaa wo to mujh par ghalib aa gaee hain ya ye kaha ke ham par ghalib aa gaee hain. shak Muhammad-bin Hoshab ko tha. ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke) mera yaqin ye hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir unke munh mein mitti jhonk de. is par meri zaban se nikla ke Allah teri naak khaak aalooda karey to na to wo kaam kar saka jiska Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya tha aur na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko takleef dena chhorta hai."
1306,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bait letey waqt ham se ye ahad bhi liya tha ke ham (maiyat par) nauha nahi karengii. lekin us iqrar ko panch aurton ke siwa aur kisi ne pura nahi kya. ye auratein Umme-Sulaim, umme-Alaa aur abu-Sabra ki sahibzadi jo Muaz ke ghar mein thin aur uske ilawa 2 auratein ya (ye kaha ke) abu-Sabra ki saahibzaadii, Muaz ki biwi aur aik dusri khatun (rz)"
1307,"jab tum janaaza dekho to khadey ho jao aur khadey raho yahan tak ke janaaza tum se aagey nikal jaey. Sufiyan ne bayan kya, unse Zohri ne bayan kya ke mujhey Salim ne apne bap Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di. aap ne farmaya ke hamein Aamir-bin-Rabee'a (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se khabar di thi. Hameedii ne ye zyadti ki hai. ''yahaan tak ke janaaza aagey nikal jaey ya rakh diya jaaey.''"
1308,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mein se koi janaaza dekhey to agar iske sath nahi chal raha hai to khada hi ho jaey yahan tak ke janaaza aagey nikal jaey ya aagey janey ki bajaey khud janaaza rakh diya jaey.
1309,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Marwan ka hath pakda aur ye donon sahib janaaza rakhey janey se pahley baith gaey. itney mein abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey aur Marwan ka hath pakad kar farmaya ke utho! Allah ki qasam! ye (abu-Huraira (rz)) jantey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein us se mana farmaya hai. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne sach kaha hai.
1310,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum log janaaza dekho to khadey ho jao aur jo shakhs janaaze ke sath chal raha ho wo us waqt tak na baithey jab tak janaaza rakh na diya jaey.
1311,hamarey samney se aik janaaza guzra to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho gaey aur ham bhi khadey ho gaey. phir ham ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! ye to Yahudi ka janaaza tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum log janaaza dekho to khadey ho jaya karo.
1312,Sahal-bin-Haneef aur Qais-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) qaadsiya mein kisi jagah baithey huey they. itney mein kuchh log idhar se aik janaaza lekar guzrey to ye donon buzurg khadey ho gaey. arz kya gaya ke janaaza to zimmiyon ka hai (jo kaafir hain) is par unhon-ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se isi tarah se aik janaaza guzra tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske liye khadey ho gaey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha gaya ke ye to Yahudi ka janaaza tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya Yahudi ki jaan nahi hai?
1313,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. aur Zakariya ne kaha unse Shabi ne aur unse ibn-abii-Lailaa ne ke Abu-Masood aur Qais (Raziallahu anhu) janaaze ke liye khadey ho jatey they.
1314,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab maiyat charpai par rakhi jati hai aur mard usey kandhon par uthatey hain to agar wo nek ho to kehta hai ke mujhey aagey ley chalo. lekin agar nek nahi to kehta hai haaye barbadi ! mujhey kahan liye ja rahe ho. us awaz ko insan ke siwa tamam Allah ki makhlooq suntii hai. agar insan kahin sun paaey to behosh ho jaey.
1315,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke janaaza lekar jald chala karo kyonke agar wo nek hai to tum usko bhalai ki taraf nazdeek kar rahe ho aur agar iske siwa hai to aik shar hai jisey tum apni gardanon se utaartey ho.
1316,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they ke jab maiyat charpai par rakhi jati hai aur log usey kandhon par uthatey hain us waqt agar wo marney wala nek hota hai to kehta hai ke mujhey jald aagey badhaatey chalo. lekin agar nek nahi hota to kehta hai ke haaye barbadi ! mujhey kahan liye ja rahe ho. uski ye awaz insan ke siwa har Allah ke makhlooq suntii hai. kahin agar insan sun paaey to behosh ho jaey.
1317,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najashi ki namaaze-janaaza padhi to main dusri ya teesri saf mein tha.
1318,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ashaab ko Najashi ki wafat ki khabar sunai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey badh gaey aur logon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey safain bana liin, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char martaba takbeer kahi."
1319,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik qabr par aaey jo aur qabron se alag thalag thi. sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne saf bandi ki aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char takbeerein kahiin. maine puchha ke ye hadis aap se kis ne bayan ki hai? unhon-ne bataya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne.
1320,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aaj habsh ke aik mard Saleh (najaashii habsh ke baadshaah) ka intiqal ho gaya hai. aao unki namaaze-janaaza padho. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir ham ne saf bandi kar li aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki namaaze-janaaza padhai. ham saf baandhey khadey they. abu-Zubair ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se naql kya ke main dusri saf mein tha.
1321,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar aik qabr par hua. maiyat ko abhi raat hi dafnaayaa gaya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke dafn Kab kya gaya hai? logon ne kaha ke pichhli raat . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey kyon nahi itlaa karaai ? logon ne arz kya ke andherii raat mein dafn kya gaya, isliye ham ne aapko jagaanaa munasib na samjhaa. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho gaey aur ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey safein bana liin. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main bhi unhiin mein tha (naabaaligh tha lekin) namaaze-janaaza mein shirkat ki."
1322,mujhey us sahabi ne khabar di thi jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik alag thalag qabr par se guzraa. wo kehta tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamari imamat ki aur ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey safain bana liin. ham ne puchha ke abu-Amr (ye Shabi ki kunniyat hai) ye aap se bayan karne waley kon sahabi hain? farmaya ke Abdullah-bin-Abbas (rz).
1323,jo dafn tak janaaze ke sath rahe usey aik qirat ka sawab milega. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Abu-Hurera hadison bahut zyada bayan kartey hain.
1324,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye irshad khud suna hai. is par ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir to ham ne bahut se qeeraaton ka nuqsan uthaayaa. (sura Zumar mein jo lafz) ( فرطت‏ ( aaya hai iske yahi mana hain maine zaaye kya.
1325,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha. (doosri sanad) ham se Ahmed bin shabeeb ne bayan kya, kaha ke mujh se mere walid ne bayan kya, unse Yunus ne bayan kya ke ibne-Shahab ne kaha ke (mujh se falan ne ye bhi hadis bayan ki) aur mujh se Abdur-Rehman Aaraj ne bhi kaha ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne janaaza mein shirkat ki phir namaaze-janaaza padhi to usey aik qirat ka sawab milta hai aur jo dafn tak sath raha to usey 2 qirat ka sawab milta hai. puchha gaya ke 2 qirat kitney hongey ? farmaya ke 2 azeem pahadon ke barabar ."
1326,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik qabr par tashrif laey. sahaba ne arz kya ke us maiyat ko pichhli raat dafn kya gaya hai. (qabr wala mard tha ya aurat thi) Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey saf bandi ki aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaaze-janaaza padhai.
1327,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Habsha ke Najashi ki wafat ki khabar di, isi din jis din unka intiqal hua tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne bhai ke liye Allah se maghfirat chaaho."
1328,aur ibne-Shahab se yun bhi riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha ke mujh se Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bayan kya ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne eidgaah mein saf bandi karaai phir ( namaaze-janaaza ki) char takbeerein kahin .
1329,"yahood Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke huzoor main apne ham-mazhab aik mard aur aurat ka, jinhoney zina kya tha, muqaddima lekar aaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se masjid ke nazdeek namaaze-janaaza padhney ki jagah ke paas unhein sangsaar kar diya gaya."
1330,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne wafat k marz mein farmaya ke yahood aur nasara par Allah ki laanat ho ke unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko masaajid bana liya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke agar aisa dar na hota to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qabr khuli rehti (aur hujre mein na hoti ( kyonke mujhey dar iska hai ke kahin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qabr bhi masjid na bana li jaey.
1331,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein aik aurat ( umme-Kab ( ki namaaze-janaaza padhi thi jiska nifaas mein intiqal ho gaya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski kamar ke muqabil khadey huey.
1332,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey aik aurat ki namaaze-janaaza padhi thi jiska zachgii ki haalat mein intiqal ho gaya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske beech mein khadey huey.
1333,Najashi ka jis din intiqal hua isi din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki wafat ki khabar di aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba ke sath eidgaah gaey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saff-bandii karaai aur char takbeerein kahiin.
1334,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne as'hama Najashi ki namaaze-janaaza padhai to char takbeerein kahiin. Yazid-bin-Harun waastii aur Abdus-Samad ne Saleem se as'hama naam naql kya hai aur Abdus-Samad ne uski mutabiat (pairavi) ki hai.
1335,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz ( janaaza ( padhi (doosri sanad) ham se Muhammad-bin Kasir ne bayan kya, kaha ke hamein Sufiyan Sory ne khabar di, unhein Sad bin Ibrahim ne, unhein Talha bin-Abdullah-bin Auf ne, unhon-ne batlaya ke maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey namaaze-janaaza padhi to aap ne sura Fatiha ( zara pukar kar) padhi. phir farmaya ke tumhen malum hona chahiye ke yahi tareeqae-nabawii hai."
1336,mujhey us sahabi ne khabar di jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik alag thalag qabr se guzrey they. qabr par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) imam baney aur sahaba ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey namaaze-janaaza padhi. Shebani ne kaha ke maine Shabi se puchha ke abu-Amr! ye aap se kis sahabi ne bayan kya tha to unhon-ne batlaya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne.
1337,"kaley rang ka aik mard ya aik kali aurat masjid ki khidmat kya karti thin, unki wafat ho gaee lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unki wafat ki khabar kisi ne nahi di. aik din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud yad farmaya ke wo shakhs dikhai nahi detaa. sahaba ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) )! unka to intiqal ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tum ne mujhey khabar kyon nahi di ? sahaba ne kaha ke ye wajhein thin (is liye aapko takleef nahi di gai) maano logon ne unko haqeer jaan kar qaabile-tawajjo nahi samjha lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke chalo mujhey unki qabr bata do. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski qabr par tashrif laey aur is par namaaze-janaaza padhi."
1338,"aadmi jab qabr mein rakha jata hai aur dafn karke iske log peeth mod kar rukhsat hotey hain to wo unke jooton ki awaz sunta hai. phir 2 Farishtey aatey hain usey bithatey hain aur poochhtey hain ke us shakhs ( Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ke mutaalliq tumhara kya aitiqaad hai? wo jawab deta hai ke main gawahi deta hun ke wo Allah ke bandey aur uske rasool hain. us jawab par us se kaha jata hai ke ye dekh jahannam ka apna aik thikana lekin Allah Taala ne jannat mein terey liye aik makan iske badley mein bana diya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir us banda momin ko jannat aur jahannam donon dikhai jati hain aur raha kaafir ya munafiq to uska jawab ye hota hai ke mujhey malum nahi, maine logon ko aik baat kehtey suna tha wahi mein bhi kehta raha. phir us se kaha jata hai ke na to ney kuchh samjha aur na (achchhey logon ki) pairwi ki. iske baad usey aik lohey ke hathodey se badey zor se maara jata hai aur wo itney bhayanak tariqa se cheekhta hai ke insan aur jinke siwa ird-gird ki tamam makhlooq suntii hai."
1339,malakul-maut (aadmii ki shakl mein) Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas bhejey gaey. wo jab aaey to Musa (Alaihissalam) ne (na pehchan kar) unhein aik zor ka tamaancha maara aur unki aankh phod daalii. wo wapas apne rab ke huzoor mein pahunchey aur arz kya ke ya Allaah! tu ney mujhey aisey bandey ki taraf bheja jo marnaa nahi chaahtaa. Allah Taala ne unki aankh pahley ki tarah kar di aur farmaya ke dobara ja aur unse keh ke aap apna hath aik bail ki peeth par rakhiye aur peeth ke jitney baal aap ke hath taley aa jayen unke har baal ke badley aik saal ki zindagi di jati hai. (Moosaa (Alaihissalam) tak jab Allah Taala ka ye paigham pahuncha to) aap ne kaha ke aey Allaah! phir kya hoga? Allah Taala ne farmaya ke phir bhi maut aanii hai. Musa (Alaihissalam) boley to abhi kyon na aa jaey. phir unhon-ne Allah se dua ki ke unhein aik patthar ki mar par arz muqaddas se qareeb kar diya jaey. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar main wahan hota to tumhen unki qabr dikhaataa ke laal teeley ke paas rastey ke qareeb hai.
1340,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aisey shakhs ki namaaze-janaaza padhi jinka intiqal raat ke waqt hua (aur usey raat hi mein dafn kar diya gaya tha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke ashaab khadey huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke mutaalliq puchha tha ke ye kin ki qabr hai. logon ne bataya ke falan ki hai jisey kal raat hi dafn kya gaya hai. phir sab ne (doosrey roz) namaaze-janaaza padhi.
1341,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar padey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kuchh beeviyon (Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) aur Umme-Habiba (rz)) ne aik girjey ka zikr kya jisey unhon-ne Habsha mein dekha tha jiska naam Mariya tha. Umme-Salma aur Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) donon Habsh ke mulk mein gaee thin. unhon-ne uski khoobsoortii aur is mein rakhi hui tasweeron ka bhi zikr kya. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar Mubarak uthaakar farmaya ke ye wo log hain ke jab unmein koi Saleh shakhs mar jata to uski qabr par masjid tameer kar detey. phir uski moorat usmein rakhtey. Allah ke nazdeek ye log saari makhlooq mein burey hain.
1342,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beti ke janaaze mein hazir they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabr par baithey huey they, maine dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon se aansu jari they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kya aisa aadmi bhi koi yahan hai jo aaj raat ko aurat ke paas na gaya ho. is par abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke main hazir hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tum qabr mein utar jao. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke wo utar gaey aur maiyat ko dafn kya. Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne bayan kya ke Fulaih ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ke) لم يقارف (ka mana ye hai ke jisne gunah na kya ho. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke sura Al-Anaam mein jo ( ليقترفوا‏ ( aaya hai iska mana yahi hai taake gunah karein."
1343,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud ke 2-2 shaheedon ko mila kar aik hi kapdey ka kafan diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) malum farmatey ke unmein Quran kisey zyada yad hai. kisi aik ki taraf ishara se bataya jata to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baghlii qabr mein usi ko aagey kartey aur farmatey ke main qiyamat mein unke haq mein shahadat doonga. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sab ko unke khoon samet dafn karne ka hukm diya. na unhein ghusl diya gaya aur na unki namaaze-janaaza padhi gaee.
1344,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din bahar tashrif laey aur Uhud ke shaheedon par is tarah Namaz padhi jaisey maiyat par padhi jati hai. phir member par tashrif laey aur farmaya, dekho main tum se pahley ja kar tumharey liye meere-saamaan banoonga aur main tum par gawah rahunga aur qism Allah ki main us waqt apne hauz ko dekh raha hun aur mujhey zameen ke khazaanon ki kunjiyaan di gaee hain ya (ye farmaya ke) mujhey zameen ki kunjiyaan di gaee hain aur qism Allah ki mujhey iska dar nahi ke mere baad tum shirk karogey balke iska dar hai ke tum log duniya hasil karne mein raghbat karogey (nateeja ye ke aakhirat se ghaafil ho jao gey) ."
1345,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud ke 2-2 shaheedon ko dafn karne mein aik sath jama farmaya tha.
1346,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein khoon samet dafn kar do yani Uhud ki ladai ke mauqe par aur unhein ghusl nahi diya tha.
1347,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Uhud ke 2-2 Shahid mardon ko aik hi kapdey mein kafan detey aur poochhtey ke unmein Quran kis ne zyada yad kya hai, phir jab kisi aik taraf ishara kar diya jata to lahad mein usi ko aagey badhaatey aur farmatey jatey ke main un par gawah hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khoon samet unhein dafn karne ka hukm diya, na unki namaaze-janaaza padhi aur na unhein ghusl diya."
1348,unmein Quran zyada kis ne hasil kya hai? jiski taraf ishara kar diya jata Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) lahad mein usi ko doosrey se aagey badhaatey . Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mere walid aur chacha ko aik hi kambal mein kafan diya gaya tha.
1349,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne Makka ko haram kya hai. na mujh se pahley kisi ke liye (yahaan qatl w khoon) halal tha aur na mere baad hoga aur mere liye bhi thodi der ke liye (fatah Makka ke din) halal hua tha. to na uski ghaas ukhaadii jaey na iske darakht qalam kiye jaaein. na yahan ke janwaron ko (shikaar ke liye) bhagaayaa jaey aur siwa us shakhs ke jo elaan karna chahta ho (ke ye giri hui cheez kiski hai) kisi ke liye wahan se koi giri hui cheez uthaanii jaaiz nahi. is par Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ''lekin us se izkhir ka istisnaa kar dijiye ke ye hamarey sunaaron ke aur hamari qabron mein kaam aati hai.'' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke magar izkhir ki ijazat hai. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat mein hai. ''hamaarii qabron aur gharon ke liye.'' aur Abaan-bin-Saaleh ne bayan kya, unse Hasan-bin-Muslim ne, unse Safiya-bint-Sheba ne ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah suna tha aur Mujahid ne Taaus ke waaste se bayan kya aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye alfaz bayan kiye. hamarey lohaaron aur gharon ke liye (izkhir ukhaadna haram se) jaaiz kar dijiye."
1350,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to Abdullah-bin-Ubai ( munafiq ( ko uski qabr mein daala ja chuka tha. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke irshad par usey qabr se nikal liya gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey apne ghutnon par rakh kar luaab dahan iske munh mein daala aur apna kurta usey pahnaayaa. ab Allah hi behtar janta hai. (ghaaliban marney ke baad aik munafiq ke sath us ehsan ki wjah ye thi ke) unhon-ne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko aik qamees pahnaaii thi (badr ki jang mein jab Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) musalmanon ke qaidi bin kar aaey they) Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke abu-Haaroon Moosaa-bin-abii-Eisaa kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke istemal mein 2 kurtey they. Abdullah ke ladkey (jo momin mukhlis they (rz)) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! mere walid ko aap wo qamees pehna dijiye jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke jism ke qareeb rehti hai. Sufiyan ne kaha log samajhtey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna kurta iske kartey ke badal pehna diya jo usne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko pahnaayaa tha.
1351,"jab jange-Uhud ka waqt qareeb aa gaya to mujhey mere bap Abdullah ne raat ko bula kar kaha ke mujhey aisa dikhai deta hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab mein sabse pahlaa maqtool mein hi hunga aur dekho Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke siwa doosra koi mujhey (apne azeezon aur waarison mein) tum se zyada azeez nahi hai, main maqrooz hun isliye tum mera qarz ada kar dena aur apni (nau (9) ( bahnon se achchha sulook karna. chunanche jab subah hui to sabse pahley mere walid hi Shahid huey. qabr mein aap ke sath maine aik doosrey shakhs ko bhi dafn kya tha. par mera dil nahi maanaa ke unhein doosrey sahib ke sath yun hi qabr mein rehney dun. chunanche 6 mahiney ke baad maine unki laash ko qabr se nikala dekha to sirf kaan thoda sa galney ke siwa baqi Sara jism isi tarah tha jaisey dafn kya gaya tha."
1352,mere bap ke sath aik hi qabr mein aik aur sahabi ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ke chacha ( dafn they. lekin mera dil is par razi nahi ho raha tha. isliye maine unki laash nikal kar dusri qabr mein dafn kar di.
1353,Uhud ke shohdaa ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik kafan mein 2-2 ko aik sath karke poochhtey they ke Quran kis ko zyada yad tha. phir jab kisi aik ki taraf ishara kar diya jata to baghlii qabr mein usey aagey kar diya jata. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ke main qiyamat ko un (ke iimaan) par gawah banoonga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein baghair ghusl diye khoon samet dafn karne ka hukm diya tha.
1354,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kuchh doosrey ashaab ke sath ibne-Sayyaad ke paas gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wo banu-Maghaala ke makaanon ke paas bachchon ke sath khelta hua mila. un dinon ibne-Sayyaad jawaanii ke qareeb tha. usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aaney ki koi khabar hi nahi hui. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par apna hath rakha to usey malum hua. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey ibne-Sayyaad ! kya tum gawahi detey ho ke main Allah ka rasool hun. ibne-Sayyaad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf dekh kar bola haan mein gawahi deta hun ke aap an-padhon ke rasool hain. phir usne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se malum kya. kya aap uski gawahi detey hain ke main bhi Allah ka rasool hoon? ye baat sun kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey chhod diya aur farmaya main Allah aur uske paighambaron par eman laya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usse puchha ke tujhey kya dikhai deta hai? ibne-Sayyaad bola ke mere paas sachchii aur jhooti donon khabrein aati hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir to tera sab kaam gadmad ho gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usse farmaya achchha maine aik baat dil mein rakhi hai wo batlaa. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sura Dukhaan ki aayat ka tasawwur kya ( فارتقب يوم تاتی السماء بدخان مبين ( ibne-Sayyaad ne kaha wo ( دخ ( hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya chal door ho to apni bisaat se aagey kabhi na badh sakega. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ya Rasulullah ! mujh ko chhod dijiye mein uski gardan mar deta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar ye dajjal hai to, to is par ghalib na hoga aur agar dajjal nahi hai to uska mar daalnaa terey liye behtar na hoga."
1355,phir aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) donon mil kar un khajoor ke darakhton mein gaey. jahan ibne-Sayyaad tha (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chahtey they ke ibne-Sayyaad aapko na dekhey aur) us se pahley ke wo aapko dekhey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghafalat mein us se kuchh baatein sun lein. aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko dekh liya. wo aik chadar odhey padaa tha. kuchh gin-gin ya phan-phan kar raha tha. lekin mushkil ye hui ke ibne-Sayyaad ki maan ne door hi se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajoor ke tanon mein chhup chhup kar ja rahe they. us ne pukar kar ibne-Sayyaad se keh diyaa: Saaf! ye naam ibne-Sayyaad ka tha. dekho Muhammad aan pahunchey . ye suntey hi wo uth khada hua. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kash! uski maan ibne-Sayyaad ko baatein karne deti to wo apna haal kholtaa . Shuaib ne apni riwayat main ( رمرمة فرفصه (aur Aqeel ne ( رمرمة‏ ( naql kya hai aur Mamar ne ( رمزة‏ ( kaha hai.
1356,"aik Yahudi ladka ( Abdul-Quddoos ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat kya karta tha, aik din wo bimar ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iska mizaaj malum karne ke liye tashrif laey aur uske sarhaaney baith gaey aur farmaya ke musalman ho jaa. us ne apne bap ki taraf dekha, bap wahin maujood tha. usne kaha ke (kya muzaayqa hai) abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jo kuchh kehtey hain maan ley. chunanche wo bachcha Islam ley aaya. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar nikley to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke shukr hai Allah paak ka jisne us bachchey ko jahannam se bacha liya."
1357,main aur meri walida (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hijrat ke baad Makka mein) kamzor musalmanon mein se they. main bachchon main aur meri walida aurton mein.
1358,ibne-Shahab har us bachchey ki jo wafat pa gaya ho namaaze-janaaza padhtey they. bhale hi wo haram hi ka bachcha kyon na ho kyonke uski paidaaish Islam ki fitrat par hui. yani is sura mein jabke iske waalidain musalman honey ke dawedar hun. agar sirf bap musalman ho aur maan ka mazhab Islam ke siwa koi aur ho jab bhi bachche ke roney ki paidaaish ke waqt agar awaz sunai deti to is par Namaz padhi jati. lekin agar paidaaish ke waqt koi awaz na aati to uski Namaz nahi padhi jati thi. balke aisey bachchey ko kachchaa hamal gir janey ke darje mein samjha jata tha. kyonke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kya hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har bachcha fitrat (Islam) par paida hota hai. phir iske maan-baap usey Yahudi ya nasrani ya majusi bana detey hain jis tarah tum dekhtey ho ke janwar sahi Salim bachcha jantaa hai. kya tum ne koi kaan kata hua bachcha bhi dekha hai? phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne us aayat ko tilawat kya. فطرة الله التي فطر Naas عليها‏‏‏ ye Allah ki fitrat hai jis par usne logon ko paida kya hai.
1359,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har bachcha fitrat par paida hota hai lekin iske maan-baap usey Yahudi ya nasrani ya majusi bana detey hain. bilkul isi tarah jaisey aik janwar aik sahi Salim janwar jantaa hai. kya tum iska koi uzu (khaas ang) ( paidaaishii taur par) kata hua dekhtey ho? phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ye Allah Taala ki fitrat hai jis par logon ko usne paida kya hai. Allah Taala ki paida ki hui chizon mein koi tabdili mumkin nahi, yahi ( دين القيم‏ ( hai."
1360,"jab abu-Taalib ki wafat ka waqt qareeb aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas tashrif laey. dekha to unke paas us waqt abu-Jahal bin Hisham aur Abdullaah-bin-Ubaii, Umayya-bin-Mugheera maujood they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke chachaa! aap aik kalima ( لا إله إلا الله ( ) Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahin) keh dijiye taake main Allah Taala ke yahan us kalima ki wjah se aap ke haq mein gawahi de sakoon. is par abu-Jahal aur Abdullaah-bin-Ubaii, Umayya-bin-Mugheera ne kaha abu-Taalib! kya tum apne bap abdul-Muttalib ke Deen se phir jaaogey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) barabar kalimae-Islaam un par pesh kartey rahe. abu-Jahal aur ibne-abii Umayya bhi apni baat dohraatey rahe. aakhir abu-Taalib ki aakhiri baat ye thi ke wo abdul-Muttalib ke Deen par hain. unhon-ne ( لا إله إلا الله ( kehney se inkar kar diya phir bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main aap ke liye istighfar karta rahunga . yahan tak ke mujhey mana na kar diya jaey, is par Allah Taala ne aayat Sura Tauba ki aayat 113 nazil farmaaii."
1361,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar aisi 2 qabron par hua jin mein azab ho raha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unko azab kisi bahut badi baat par nahi ho raha hai sirf ye ke unmein aik shakhs peshab se nahi bachta tha aur doosra shakhs chughal khorii kya karta tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ki aik harii dali li aur uske 2 tukdey karke donon qabr par eik-eik tukda gaad diya. logon ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! aap ne aisa kyon kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke shayad us waqt tak ke liye in par azab kuchh halka ho jaey jab tak ye khushk na hun.
1362,ham Baqee gharqad mein aik janaaze ke sath they. itney main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur baith gaey. ham bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ird-gird baith gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik chhadi thi jis se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zameen kuredney lagey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein se koi aisa nahi ya koi jaan aisi nahi jiska thikana jannat aur dozakh donon jagah na likha gaya ho aur ye bhi ke wo nek bakht hogi ya bad-bakht. is par aik sahabi ne arz kya ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! phir kyon na ham apni taqdeer par bharosa kar lein aur amal chhod dein kyonke jiska naam nek daftar mein likha hai wo zaroor nek kaam ki taraf rujoo hoga aur jiska naam bad-bakhton mein likha hai wo zaroor badi ki taraf jaeyga Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke baat ye hai ke jinka naam nek bakhton mein hai unko achchhey kaam karne mein hi aasani malum hoti hai aur bad-bakhton ko burey kaamon mein aasani nazar aati hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aayat ki tilawat ki) فأما من أعطى واتقى‏ ( الآية‏ .
1363,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs Islam ke siwa kisi aur Deen par honey ki jhooti qism qasdan khaaey to wo waisaa hi ho jaeyga jaisa ke usne apne liye kaha hai aur jo shakhs apne ko dhaar daar cheez se zabah kar ley usey jahannam mein usi hathiyar se azab hota rahega.
1364,"isi (Basra ki) masjid mein hadis bayan ki thi, na ham us hadis ko bhooley hain aur na ye dar hai ke Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jhoot baandha hoga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik shakhs ko zakhm laga, usne ( zakhm ki takleef ki wjah se) khud ko mar dala. is par Allah Taala ne farmaya ke mere bandey ne jaan nikalney mein mujh par jaldi ki. uski saza mein, main is par jannat haram karta hun."
1365,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs khud apna gala ghont kar jaan de daalta hai wo jahannam mein bhi apna gala ghont'taa rahega aur jo barchhey ya teer se apne taiin (aapko) maarey wo dozakh mein bhi is tarah apne ( aapko ( taiin maarta rahega.
1366,"jab Abdullaah-bin-Ubaii-ibne-salool maraa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is par namaaze-janaaza ke liye kaha gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab us iraadey se khadey huey to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf badh kar arz kya ya Rasulullah ! aap ibne-abi ki namaaze-janaaza padhatey hain halanke us ne falan din falan baat kahi thi aur falan din falan baat. main uski kufr ki baatein ginney laga. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye sun kar muskuraa diye aur farmaya Umar! us waqt peechhey hat jao. lekin jab main baar-baar apni baat dohraataa raha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya ke mujhey Allah ki taraf se ikhtiyar de diya gaya hai, maine Namaz padhaanii pasand ki agar mujhey malum ho jaey ke 70 martaba se zyada martaba uske liye maghfirat maangney par usey maghfirat mil jaeygi to uske liye itni hi zyada maghfirat maangonga. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski namaaze-janaaza padhai aur wapas honey ke thodi der baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par sura Tauba ki 2 aayatein nazil huin. ''kisi bhi munafiq ki maut par uski namaaze-janaaza aap hargiz na padhaaiye.'' aayat ( وهم فاسقون‏ ( tak aur uski qabr par bhi mat khadey hon, un logon ne Allah aur uske rasool ki baton ko nahi maanaa aur marey bhi to naafarmaan reh kar. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke huzoor apni isi din ki dilairii par tajjub hota hai. halanke Allah aur uske rasool (har maslihat ko) zyada jantey hain."
1367,"sahaba ka guzar aik janaaze par hua, log uski tareef karne lagey (ke kya achchha aadmi tha) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye sun kar farmaya ke wajib ho gaee. phir doosrey janazey ka guzar hua to log uski burai karne lagey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke wajib ho gaee. is par umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha ke kya cheez wajib ho gaee ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis maiyat ki tum logon ne tareef ki hai uske liye to jannat wajib ho gaee aur jiski tum ne burai ki hai uske liye dozakh wajib ho gaee. tum log zameen mein Allah Taala ke gawah ho."
1368,"mein Madina hazir hua. un dinon wahan aik bimari phail rahi thi. main umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein tha ke aik janaaza samney se guzraa. log us maiyat ki tareef karne lagey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke wajib ho gaee phir aik aur janaaza guzraa, log uski bhi tareef karne lagey. us martaba bhi aap ne aisa hi farmaya ke wajib ho gaee. phir tesraa janaaza nikla, log uski burai karne lagey, aur us martaba bhi aap ne yahi farmaya ke wajib ho gaee. abul-Aswad ne bayan kya ke maine puchha ke ameerul-momineen kya cheez wajib ho gaee ? aap ne farmaya ke maine us waqt wahi kaha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke jis musalman ki achai par char shakhs gawahi de dein Allah usey jannat mein dakhil karega . ham ne kaha aur agar teen gawahi dein? aap ne farmaya ke teen par bhi, phir ham ne puchha aur agar 2 musalman gawahi dein ? aap ne farmaya ke 2 par bhii. phir ham ne ye nahi puchha ke agar aik musalman gawahi de to kiya?"
1369,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke momin jab apni qabr mein bithaya jata hai to uske paas Farishtey aatey hain. wo shahadat deta hai ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke rasool hain. to ye Allah ke us farman ki tabeer hai jo sura Ibrahim mein hai ke Allah eman walon ko duniya ki zindagi aur aakhirat mein theek baat yani tauheed par mazbut rakhta hai.
1370,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuwein walon (jis mein badr ke mushrik maqtooleen ko daal diya gaya tha) ke qareeb aaey aur farmaya tumharey Malik ne jo tum se sachcha wada kya tha usey tum logon ne pa liya. logon ne arz kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mardon ko khitab kartey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum kuchh unse zyada sunney waley nahi ho albatta wo jawab nahi de saktey.
1371,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badr ke kaafiron ko ye farmaya tha ke main jo unse kaha karta tha ab unko malum hua hoga ke wo sach hai. aur Allah ne Sura Rome mein farmaayaa (إنك لا تسمع الموتى‏) aey paighambar ! to mardon ko nahi suna sakta.
1372,aik Yahudi aurat unke paas aai. usne azaabe-qabr ka zikr chhed diya aur kaha ke Allah tujh ko azaabe-qabr se mehfooz rakhey. is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se azaabe-qabr ke barey mein malum kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iska jawab ye diya ke yahan azaabe-qabr haq hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir maine kabhi aisa nahi dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi Namaz padhi ho aur is mein azaabe-qabr se Allah ki panah na mangi ho. ghandar ne ( azaabe-qabr haq (ke alfaz zyada kiye.
1373,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutbe ke liye khadey huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabr ke imtihaan ka zikr kya jahan insan jaanchaa jata hai. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iska zikr kar rahe they, to musalmanon ki hichkiyaan bandh gain ."
1374,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aadmi jab apni qabr mein rakha jata hai aur janaaze mein Sharik hone-waale log usse rukhsat hotey hain to abhi wo unke jooton ki awaz sunta hota hai ke 2 Farishtey (munkar-nakeer) uske paas aatey hain, wo usey bitha kar poochhtey hain ke us shakhs yani Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey main to kya aqeeda rakhta tha? momin to ye kahega ke main gawahi deta hun ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke bandey aur uske rasool hain. us jawab par usse kaha jaeyga ke to ye dekh apna jahannam ka thikana lekin Allah Taala ne iske badle main tumharey liye jannat mein thikana de diya. us waqt usey jahannam aur jannat donon thikaaney dikhaaey jaengey. Qatada ne bayan kya ke uski qabr khub kushaada kar di jaeygi. (jis se aaraam w raahat miley) phir Qatada ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis bayan karni shuru ki, farmaya aur munafiq w kaafir se jab kaha jaeyga ke us shakhs ke barey main to kya kehta tha to wo jawab dega ke mujhey kuchh malum nahi, main bhi wahi kehta tha jo doosrey log kehtey they. phir usse kaha jaeyga na to ney jaanney ki koshish ki aur na samajhney walon ki raey par chalaa. phir usey lohey ke gurzon se badi zor se maara jaeyga ke wo cheekh padega aur uski cheekh ko jin aur insanon ke siwa uske aas-paas ki tamam makhlooq sunegii."
1375,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina se bahar tashrif le gaey, suraj ghurub ho chuka tha, us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik awaz sunai di. ( yahudiyon par azaabe-qabr ki) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Yahudi par uski qabr mein azab ho raha hai. aur Nazar-bin-Shumail ne bayan kya ke hamein Shoba ne khabar di, unse Aun ne bayan kya, unhon-ne apne bap abu-Hujaifa se suna, unhon-ne Bara se suna, unhon-ne Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
1376,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko qabr ke azab se panah maangtey suna.
1377,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is tarah dua kartey they اللهم إني أعوذ بك من عذاب القبر ، Mina padhi. ومن عذاب النار ، Mina padhi. ومن فتنة المحيا والممات ، Mina padhi. ومن فتنة المسيح الدجال ''aey Allah ! main qabr ke azab se teri panah chahta hun aur dozakh ke azab se aur zindagi aur maut ki aazmaaishon se aur kaaney dajjal ki bula se teri panah chahta hoon''.
1378,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar 2 qabron par hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un donon ke mardon par azab ho raha hai aur ye bhi nahi ke kisi badi aham baat par ho raha hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan! unmein aik shakhs to chughal khorii kya karta tha aur doosra peshab se bchney ke liye ehtiyat nahi karta tha. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik harii tahnii li aur uske 2 tukdey karke donon ki qabron par gaad diya aur farmaya ke shayad jab tak ye khushk na hon unka azab kam ho jaey.
1379,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mein se koi shakhs mar jata hai to uska thikana usey subah w Sham dikhaya jata hai. agar wo jannati hai to jannat walon main aur jo dozakhi hai to dozakh walon mein. phir kaha jata hai ye tera thikana hai yahan tak ke qiyamat ke din Allah tujh ko uthaaega.
1380,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab janaaza taiyaar ho jata hai phir mard usko apni gardanon par utha letey hain to agar wo murda nek ho to kehta hai ke yahan aagey liye chalo mujhey badhaatey chalo aur agar nek nahi hota to kehta hai. haaye rey kharaabii! mera janaaza kahan liye ja rahe ho. us awaz ko insan ke siwa tamam Allah ki makhlooq suntii hai. agar kahin insan sun paaein to behosh ho jaaein.
1381,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis musalman ke bhi teen nabaligh bachchey mar jayen to Allah Taala apne Fazal w rehmat se jawan bachchon par karega, unko bahisht mein ley jaeyga"
1382,jab Ibrahim (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saahibzaadey) ka intiqal hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bahisht mein unke liye aik doodh pilaaney wali hai.
1383,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushrikon ke nabaligh bachchon ke barey mein puchha gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne jab unhein paida kya tha usi waqt wo khub janta tha ke ye kya amal karengey.
1384,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushrikon ke nabaligh bachchon ke barey mein puchha gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah khub janta hai jo bhi wo amal karne waley huey.
1385,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya har bachche ki paidaaish fitrat par hoti hai phir iske maan-baap usey Yahudi ya nasrani ya majusi bana detey hain bilkul is tarah jaisey janwar ke bachchey sahi Salim hotey hain. kya tum ne (paidaaishii taur par) koi unke jism ka hissa kata hua dekha hai.
1386,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ( fajr ( padhney ke baad) umuman ( hamari taraf munh karke baith jatey aur poochhtey ke aaj raat kisi ne koi khuwab dekha ho to bayan karo. rawi ne kaha ke agar kisi ne koi khuwab dekha hota to usey wo bayan kar deta aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski tabeer Allah ko jo manzoor hoti bayan farmatey. aik din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mamool (routine) ke mutabiq ham se malum farmaya kya aaj raat kisi ne tum mein koi khuwab dekha hai? ham ne kaha ke kisi ne nahi dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya lekin maine aaj raat aik khuwab dekha hai ke 2 aadmi mere paas aaey. unhon-ne mere hath thaam liye aur wo mujhey arze-muqaddas ki taraf ley gaey. (aur wahan se aalame-baalaa ki mujh ko sair karaaii) wahan kya dekhta hun ke aik shakhs to betha hua hai aur aik shakhs khada hai aur uske hath mein (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke) hamarey kuchh ashaab ne (ghaaliban Abbaas-bin-Fuzail isqaatii ne Musa bin Ismail se yun riwayat kya hai) lohey ka aankdaa tha jisey wo baithney waley ke jabdey mein daal kar uske sar ke peechhey tak cheer detaa, phir doosrey jabdey ke sath bhi isi tarah karta tha. us doran mein uska pahlaa jabdaa sahi aur apni aslii haalat par aa jata aur phir pahley ki tarah wo usey dobara cheertaa. maine puchha ke ye kya ho raha hai? mere sath ke donon aadmiyon ne kaha ke aagey chalein. chunanche ham aagey badhey to aik aisey shakhs ke paas aaey jo sar ke bal leta hua tha aur doosra shakhs aik bada sa patthar liye uske sar par khada tha. us patthar se wo letey huey shakhs ke sar ko kuchal deta tha. jab wo uske sar par patthar maarta to sar par lag kar wo patthar door chala jata aur wo usey ja kar utha laataa . abhi patthar lekar wapas bhi nahi aata tha ke sar dobara durust ho jata. bilkul waisaa hi jaisa pahley tha. wapas aa kar wo phir usey maarta . maine puchha ke ye kon log hain? un donon ne jawab diya ke abhi aur aagey chalein . chunanche ham aagey badhey to aik tannoor jaisey garhey ki taraf chaley. jiske uper ka hissa to tang tha lekin nichey se khub chaudaa. nichey aag bhadak rahi thi. jab aag ke sholey bhadak kar uper ko uthtey to usmein jalney waley log bhi uper uth aatey aur aisa malum hota ke ab wo bahar nikal jaeinge lekin jab sholey dab jatey to wo log bhi nichey chaley jatey. ustannoor mein nangey mard aur auratein thin. maine us mauqe par bhi puchha ke ye kya hai? lekin us martaba bhi jawab yahi mila kaha ke abhi aur aagey chalein, ham aagey chaley. ab ham khoon ki aik nehar ke uper they nehar ke andar aik shakhs khada tha aur uske beech mein (Yazeed-bin-Haaroon aur Wahab-bin-Jareer ne Jareer-bin-Haazim ke waaste se ( وسطه النهر (ke bajaey (Shatun-Nahar) nehar ke kinarey ke alfaz naql kiye hain) aik shakhs tha. jiske samney patthar rakha hua tha. nehar ka aadmi jab bahar nikalnaa chahta to patthar wala shakhs iske munh par itni zor se patthar maarta ke wo apni pehli jagah par chala jata aur isi tarah jab bhi wo nikalney ki koshish karta wo shakhs iske munh par patthar itni hi zor se phir maarta ke wo apni aslii jagah par nehar mein chala jata. maine puchha ye kya ho raha hai? unhon-ne jawab diya ke abhi aur aagey chalein. chunanche ham aur aagey badhey aur aik harey bharey baagh mein aaey. jis mein aik bahut bada darakht tha us darakht ki jad mein aik badi umr waley buzurg baithey huey they aur unke sath kuchh bachchey bhi baithey huey they. darakht se qareeb hi aik shakhs apne aagey aag sulgaa raha tha. wo mere donon sathi mujhey lekar us darakht par chadhey. is tarah wo mujhey aik aisey ghar mein le gaey ke us se zyada Husain aur khoobsurat aur ba-barkat ghar maine kabhi nahi dekha tha. us ghar mein boodhey, jawaan, auratein aur bachchey (sab hi qism ke log) they. mere sathi mujhey us ghar se nikal kar phir aik aur darakht par chadhaa kar mujhey aik aur doosrey ghar mein le gaey jo bahut hi zyada khoobsurat aur behtar tha. usmein bhi bahut se boodhey aur jawan they. maine apne sathiyon se kaha tum logon ne mujhey raat bhar khub sair karaai . kya jo kuchh maine dekha uski tafseel bhi kuchh batlaaogey? unhon-ne kaha haan wo jo aap ne dekha tha us aadmi ka jabdaa lohey ke aankdey se phaadaa ja raha tha to wo jhoota aadmi tha jo jhooti baatein bayan kya karta tha. us se wo jhooti baatein doosrey log suntey. is tarah aik jhooti baat door-door tak phail jaya karti thi. usey qiyamat tak yahi azab hota rahega. jis shakhs ko aap ne dekha ke iska sar kuchlaa ja raha tha to wo aik aisa insan tha jisey Allah Taala ne Quran ka ilm diya tha lekin wo raat ko padaa sota rehta aur din main is par amal nahi karta tha. usey bhi ye azab qiyamat tak hota rahega aur jinhein aap ne tannoor mein dekha to wo zinaakaar they. aur jisko aap ne nehar mein dekha wo sood khaane waala tha aur wo buzurg jo darakht ki jad mein baithey huey they wo Ibrahim they aur unke ird-gird waley bachchey, logon ki nabaligh aulad thi aur jo shakhs aag jalaa raha tha wo dozakh ka darogha tha aur wo ghar jis mein aap pahley dakhil huey jannat mein aam mominon ka ghar tha aur ye ghar jis mein aap ab khadey hain, ye shohdaa ka ghar hai aur main Jibreel hun aur ye mere sath meekaaeel hain. achchha ab apna sar uthao maine jo sar uthaya to kya dekhta hun ke mere uper badal ki tarah koi cheez hai. mere sathiyon ne kaha ke ye aapka makan hai. is par maine kaha ke phir mujhey apne makan mein janey do. unhon-ne kaha ke abhi aap ki umr baqi hai jo aap ne poori nahi ki agar aap wo poori kar letey to apne makan mein aa jatey."
1387,"main (waalid maajid) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein (unki marzul-maut mein) hazir hui to aap ne puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tum logon ne kitney kapdon ka kafan diya tha? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne jawab diya ke teen safaid dhuley huey kapdon kaa. aapko kafan mein qameez aur amama nahi diya gaya tha aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse ye bhi puchha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat kis din hui thi. unhon-ne jawab diya ke peer ke din. phir puchha ke aaj kon sa din hai? unhon-ne kaha aaj peer ka din hai. aap ne farmaya ke phir mujhey bhi ummeed hai ke ab se raat tak mein bhi rukhsat ho jaaunga. iske baad aap ne apna kapda dekha jisey marz ke doran mein aap pahan rahe they. us kapdey par zafran ka dhabba laga hua tha. aap ne farmaya mere us kapdey ko dho lena aur uske sath 2 aur mila lena phir mujhey kafan unhiin ka dena. maine kaha ke ye to puraanaa hai. farmaya ke zinda aadmi naey ( kapdey (ka murdey se zyada mustahiq hai, ye to peep aur khoon ki nazar ho jaeyga phir mangal ki raat ka kuchh hissey guzarney par aap ka intiqal hua aur subah honey se pahley aapko dafn kya gaya."
1388,aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke meri maan ka achcha intiqal ho gaya aur mera khayal hai ke agar unhein baat karne ka mauqa milta to wo kuchh na kuchh khairat kartin . agar main unki taraf se kuchh khairat kar dun to kya unhein iska sawab milega? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan milega.
1389,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne maut ke marz mein maano ijazat lena chahtey they ( malum farmatey ( aaj meri baari kin ke yahan hai. kal kin ke yahan hogi ? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari ke din ke mutaalliq khayal farmatey they ke bahut din baad aaeygii . chunanche jab meri baari aai to Allah Taala ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Rooh us haal mein qabz ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere seeney se tek lagaey huey they aur mere hi ghar mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dafn kiye gaey.
1390,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne us marz ke mauqe par farmaya tha jis se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jaan-bar na ho sakey they ke Allah Taala ki yahood w nasara par laanat ho. unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko masaajid bana liya. agar ye dar na hota to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qabr bhi khuli rehney di jati. lekin dar iska hai ke kahin usey bhi log sajdagaah na bana lin aur Hilal se riwayat hai ke Urwa-bin-Zubair ne meri kunniyat (abu-Awaana yani awaana ke waalid) rakh di thi warna mere koi aulad na thi. hamse Muhammad ne bayan kya, kaha ke hamein Abdullah ne khabar di, kaha ke hamein Abu-Bakar bin Ayash ne khabar di aur unse Sufiyan timaar ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qabr Mubarak dekhi hai jo kohan ki tarah ubhra hua hai. hamse farwa-bin-abii-maghraa ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne bayan kya, unse Hisham-bin-Urwa ne, unse unke walid ne ke Waleed-bin-abdul-Malik-bin-Marwaan ke ahad hukumat mein (jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hujra Mubarak ki) diwar giri aur log usey (zyaada oonchii) uthaney lagey to wahan aik qadam zahir hua. log ye samajh kar ghabraa gaey ke ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka qadam Mubarak hai. koi shakhs aisa nahi tha jo qadam ko pehchan sakta. aakhir Urwa-bin-Zubair ne bataya ke nahi Allah gawah hai ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka qadam nahi hai balke ye to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka qadam hai."
1391,aap ne Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko wasiiyat ki thi ke mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon ke sath dafn na karna. balke meri dusri sokanon ke sath Baqee gharqad mein mujhey dafn karna. mein ye nahi chahti ke unke sath meri bhi tareef hua kare.
1392,"meri maujoodgii mein Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke aey Abdullaah! Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein ja aur keh ke Umar-bin-Khattab ne aapko salam kaha hai aur phir unse malum karna ke kya mujhey mere donon sathiyon ke sath dafn honey ki aap ki taraf se ijazat mil sakti hai? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke maine us jagah ko apne liye pasand kar rakha tha lekin aaj main apne par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko tarjeeh deti hun. jab ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) wapas aaey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne malum kya ke kya paigham laey ho? kaha ke ameerul-momineen unhon-ne aapko ijazat de di hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ye sun kar boley ke us jagah dafn honey se zyada mujhey aur koi cheez azeez nahi thi. lekin jab meri Rooh qabz ho jaey to mujhey utha kar ley jana aur phir dobara Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko mera salam pahuncha kar unse kehna ke umr ne aap se ijazat chahi hai. agar us waqt bhi wo ijazat de dein to mujhey wahin dafn kar denaa, warna musalmanon ke qabristaan mein dafn kar dena. main us khilafat ka un chand sahaba se zyada aur kisi ko mustahiq nahi samajhta jin se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni wafat ke waqt tak khush aur razi rahe. wo hazraat mere baad jisey bhi khaleefa banaaein, khaleefa wahi hoga aur tumharey liye zaroori hai ke tum apne khaleefa ki baatein tawajjoh se suno aur uski itaat karo. aap ne us mauqe par Usmaan, Ali, tal'ha, zubair, Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf aur Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ke naam liye. itney mein aik Ansari naujawaan dakhil hua aur kaha ke aey ameerul-momineen aapko bashaarat ho, izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ki taraf se, aap ka Islam mein pahley dakhil honey ki wjah se jo martaba tha wo aapko malum hai. phir jab aap khaleefa huey to aap ne insaf kya. phir aap ne shahadat paaii. umr (Raziallahu anhu) boley mere bhai ke betey! kash! unki wjah se main barabar chhoot jaun. na mujhey koi azab ho aur na koi sawaab. haan main apne baad aaney waley khaleefa ko wasiiyat karta hun ke wo muhajireen awwaleen ke sath achchha bartaw rakhey, unke huquq pahchaaney aur unki izzat ki hifazat karey aur main usey Ansar ke barey mein bhi achchha bartaw rakhney ki wasiiyat karta hun. ye wo log hain jinhoney eman walon ko apne gharon mein jagah di. (meri wasiiyat hai ke) unke achchhey logon ke sath bhalai ki jaey aur unmein jo burey hon unse darguzar kya jaey aur main hone-waale khaleefa ko wasiiyat karta hun us zimme-dari ko pura karne ki jo Allah aur rasool ki zimme-dari hai (yani ghair muslimon ki jo Islami hukumat ke tehet zindagi guzaartey hain) ke unse kiye gaey wa'don ko pura kya jaey. unhein bacha kar lada jaey aur taqat se zyada un par koi baar na daala jaey."
1393,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, mardon ko bura na kaho kyonke unhon-ne jaisa amal kya iska badla pa liya. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ali-bin-ja'ad, Muhammad-bin-Ar-ara aur ibne-abii-Adii ne Shoba se ki hai. aur uski riwayat Abdullah-bin Abdul-Quddoos ne Aamash se aur Muhammad-bin Anas ne bhi Aamash se ki hai."
1394,abu-Lahab ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke sarey din tujh par barbadi ho. is par ye aayat utrii تبت يدا أبي لهب وتب‏ yaanii toot gaey hath abu-Lahab ke aur wo khud hi barbad ho gaya.
